{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_001", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角转生到异世界后，系统奖励了他一个'神秘的宝箱'，但需要等级99才能打开。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角在打败魔王后升到了99级，打开宝箱后发现里面是一张回家的车票。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_002", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "游戏中的新手村有一个不发布任务的NPC老人，整天在村口晒太阳。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老人是上一代的勇者，他已经完成了自己的使命，在这里安享晚年。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_003", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角的技能面板上有一个灰色技能叫'???'，描述是'只有在最关键的时刻才能使用'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "在最终决战中，主角为了保护同伴，'???'技能激活了——'羁绊'，效果是借用所有同伴的力量。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_004", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "公会仓库中有一把无人能装备的武器，属性全是问号。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "这把武器需要全职业满级才能装备——它是游戏制作人的彩蛋武器。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_005", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "电竞比赛的主办方在奖杯上刻了一行小字：'献给真正热爱游戏的人。'", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "奖杯底部藏着一个U盘——里面是第一届冠军队伍传承下来的战术手册。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_006", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角在异世界的旅馆中住了一晚后，发现自己的属性点涨了1点。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "旅馆的床是用世界树的木材做的——睡在上面可以缓慢增长属性。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
