{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_009", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角在竞技场中遇到一个ID叫'LAST_BOSS'的玩家，对方实力深不可测。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "'LAST_BOSS'是游戏AI的测试账号——它在收集玩家数据来优化BOSS战。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_010", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "游戏中的某个地图上有一个上锁的小屋，钥匙在全世界随机掉落。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "小屋中住着一个隐居的NPC——他是游戏的设计者之一，选择了活在游戏中。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
