{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_026", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角在异世界的魔王城门口看到了一盏熄灭的路灯——异世界没有电。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "路灯是另一个穿越者留下的——他是来自现代世界的工程师。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
