{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_032", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角的异世界冒险故事在网上连载，评论区有一个神秘账号总在剧透。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "剧透者是未来的主角——他通过时间魔法回到了过去看自己的传记。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_033", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "主角在游戏中做日常任务时帮助了一个看起来弱小的NPC。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那个NPC是游戏最强的隐藏BOSS——他伪装成新手来测试玩家的心性。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_light_novel_034", "genre": "light_novel", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "异世界的魔法学院中有一间永远上锁的教室，没人知道里面有什么。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "教室里封印着学院创始人的'失败作'——一个过于强大而无法控制的禁咒。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
